  <tr>
	<td bgcolor="#202050">
	    <font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" size="-2"><br>
		[This was sent in...]<p>Greetings my assembled dark brethren. I am Dravic D'Rakken, proud member of <br>the Indigo Brotherhood and founder of the Intemptestia Nox. I realize that <br>you probably have not heard of this fine organization as of yet. This is <br>unfortunate but true. There is a reason for our hiding in obscurity though. <br>We lurked in the shadows, gathering our resources and attracting key <br>members, preparing for the day we would be ready to go public and claim <br>Norrath as our own. That day is come now! I and my accomplice, the ogre <br>Garag Van'Guldor, are currently seeking new members to fill our ranks. Too <br>long have the Teir'dal been struggling in the world of Karana, but despair <br>no longer! The Nox will bring a new age of glory upon the lands of Norrath, <br>but only with YOUR help. So come now and join!<br>An out of character note: Now to toss aside the big words and give you the <br>bare bones :-) The Intemptestia Nox is a new evil roleplaying guild on the <br>Karana Server and we need more Teir'dal members. Even if you are not <br>interested in joining please visit our site just to see the sights, and to <br>read the superbly written charter and history (written by yours truly). Our <br>site is at <A HREF="http://www.geocities.com/smashemup_troll/">http://www.geocities.com/smashemup_troll</A> or you can email your questions <br>and comments to us at <A HREF="mailto:intemptestianox@hotmail.com">intemptestianox@hotmail.com</A>. Thank you for your time <br>and I hope to hear from you soon.<p>-Dravic D'Rakken<br>
		<p><font size="1">
		<STRONG>- <a href="mailto:keeper@neriak.com">The Keeper</a></STRONG></font></font></td>
